      "message": "\u003e\u003e add UpdateToken at the time the artifact uploader is constructed\nI will send a separate CL to add UpdateToken to ArtifactUploader.\n\n\u003e\u003e Just pass the entire Artifact object through instead of exploding it into the args\nInitially, ArtifactUploader was implemented with a single Upload(ctx, task.artName, task.art), but I changed the function signature such that it takes `contents []byte` or `filePath string` instead.\n\nThe intent is to make ArtifactUploader self-contained without ResultSink so that an application may use ArtifactUploader to upload an artifact without importing any module/protos from ResultSink.\n\n+nodir@, please correct me, if anything incorrect.",
