      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e\u003e why ArtifactUploader is in sink package if our intention is to make it sink-agnostic?\n\nI wanted to have it tested with ResultSink first, and then move it out of ResultSink folder with a new package name once there are actual use cases. I wrote it as if it was an independent, public package so that it would be easy to move it out with a minimum change.\n\nI filed https://crbug.com/1099560 for the work.",
